---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '@/components/Button.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About erzoc.dev and how it's built.">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>This site uses <strong>Astro</strong> with file-based routing and reusable components.</p>

  <h2>File routing</h2>
  <p>Routes come from <code>src/pages/</code>:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>index.astro</code> → /</li>
    <li><code>about.astro</code> → /about/</li>
    <li><code>blog/index.astro</code> → /blog/</li>
    <li><code>blog/[slug].astro</code> → /blog/:slug</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Storage & data</h2>
  <p>Site nav and footer text live in <code>src/data/site.json</code>. Blog content is in <code>src/content/blog/</code> (content collections).</p>

  <p><Button href="/">Back home</Button></p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  ul { margin: 0.5rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  code {
    font-size: 0.9em;
    background: #eee;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  h2 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
</style>
